-- Hochtief Unit Wins Order to Manage Modernization of Madison Square Garden
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-07-16T08:31:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/hochtief-unit-wins-order-to-manage-modernization-of-madison-square-garden.html

          
          
             Hochtief AG’s Turner unit has won a
contract to provide construction management services for the
modernization and “full-scale transformation” of Madison
Square Garden in New York. The value of the contract remains
confidential, the company said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        